products.title: Grazia White Vertical Blind
products.description: A classic choice for dressing your windows in style, without interfering with your carefully chosen decor, white blinds are a timeless favourite. This sleek little number gives that classic a contemporary twist though, with its clean lines, slimline components and crisp chic.
